ory training and provide a list of all chemicals to be brought used or stored in the sample preparation laboratory for details contact cynthia patty 650 926 3925 scientific applications selected results november 2009 stanford led research helps overcome barrier for organic electronics september 2009 leslie jimison receives klein award august 2009 understanding charge transport in plastic electronics june 2008 electronics go organic march 2008 novel ferroelectric nanostructures for nanoelectronic devices february 2008 controlling the wave november 2006 x ray diffraction and the fight against heart disease august 2006 hydrogen key to a sustainable future engineering notes ssrl beamlines user admin safety last updated 28 jan 2011 page editor nikola stojanovic
